  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate whether ultrasound performed during outpatient visit is effective in
      early diagnosis of fatty liver.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      All patients presenting to dedicated hepatology clinic with concern for fatty liver will be
      evaluated by ultrasound. This will be compared with standard imaging performed for this
      condition. The data will be compared for effectiveness of outpatient evaluation with
      dedicated imaging currently practiced
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
